      <h2>About</h2>
      <p><strong>Learning is about more than accumulating knowledge</strong> - it's about acheiving greatness, however that may be defined for one's circumstances. <em>Master Of Thought</em> is a compilation of timeless principles and current tools needed for correct thinking and self-mastery - carrying the spirit of the text, <a href="/as-a-man-thinketh"><em>As a Man Thinketh</em></a>, by James Allen.</p>
      <p>This site is being developed in conjunction with <a href="http://learnerinterests.com/">Learner Interests</a>, a resource to help parents pursue lifelong learning with their children, however the resources here on <em>Master of Thought</em> are equally applicable to anyone.</p>

